   Goodbye
     * Linux Journal

   Linux Journal Ceases Publication: An Awkward Goodbye

IMPORTANT NOTICE FROM LINUX JOURNAL, LLC:

On August 7, 2019, Linux Journal shut its doors for good. All staff were laid
off and the company is left with no operating funds to continue in any
capacity. The website will continue to stay up for the next few weeks,
hopefully longer for archival purposes if we can make it happen.

–Linux Journal, LLC

